data.description: Certificate of occupancy just received! Construction complete /move in ready! Huge level yard almost 1/2-acre new construction with an easy commute to Highway 85 or Hwy 90 on the south side of town! This three-bedroom two bath is complete for a quick move in! The raised ceilings in the living room and the covered back porch give these open areas a great place for a BBQ or family fun!  Enjoy the huge master bedroom and master closet. Bring your garden and your family to see this new home today! Don't forget the Huge back yard! Bring your camper, boat and BBQ grill!
